Go to https://brilliant.org/nutshell/ to dive deeper into these topics and more with a free 30-day trial + 20% off the premium subscription! 
This video was sponsored by Brilliant. Thanks a lot for the support!

Grab your Curiosity Guide  now, only available from the kurzgesagt shop: https://shop.kgs.link/im-curious 
Its lovingly packed with epic quests to get you moving, thinking, and seeing the world in a whole new way.

All changes and the link to the original video are listed in 
Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/sources-workoutparadox

Exercising doesnt help you lose weight. In fact, it barely changes your daily calorie burn.
Welcome to the workout paradox!
Lets dive into the science of how your body actually handles calories and sabotages your best efforts to burn them.

This video was created with scientific advice by Dr. Mike Israetel:
https://www.youtube.com/@RenaissancePeriodization
